{
  "id": 6680245553987584,
  "name": "WebGPU: Uniform buffer standard layout",
  "summary": "Functionality added to the WebGPU spec after its first shipment in a browser.\n\nUniform buffers declared in WGSL shaders are no longer required to have 16-byte alignment on array elements, or to pad nested structure offsets to a multiple of 16 bytes.",
