  "rollout_plan_displayname": "Will ship enabled for all users",
  "motivation": "This feature simplifies the use of uniform buffers in WGSL shaders by unifying their constraints with those of storage buffers. Without this, developers are required to align all array elements to 16 bytes and pad nested structures to achieve a 16-byte offset.\n\n",
